item.title: CVE-2024-6517|2024-09-26T06:00:02.953Z -- unknown -- contact%20form%207%20math%20captcha
item.description: The Contact Form 7 Math Captcha WordPress plugin through 2.0.1 does not sanitise and escape a parameter before outputting it back in the page, leading to a Reflected Cross-Site Scripting which could be used against high privilege users.
